SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A6F9Emg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FA6F9Emg.png&h=1f58a7df&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mS94Fjr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmS94Fjr.png&h=cd529d60&s={SIZE}\" />林明禎 v Margot Robbie<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/R8Ljujw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FR8Ljujw.png&h=842f3f46&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃分組賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幅相用小丑女可能多票D</blockquote><br />\n你不如話華爾街狼人全裸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過要變左[url][/url],唔係會bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊幅圖都唔會嬴林明禎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e97cb19383ce4c0fa18425b5a5a32eaa34740b","tid":397661,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9540e3c35a4eb615efb4414286fa5d0a1928f5db","tid":397661,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d811396273b803e355bbde41712157becd751c3f","tid":397661,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply